  "detailed_description": "Collect your favorite tiles, manipulate your draws and discards, and aim for continuous wins and high scores!<br>Yes, like the endless sky that knows no bounds!<br><strong>Sky's The Limit MAH-JONG</strong> offers mechanisms that make the impossible possible, something you can't experience in regular Mahjong. How you use these mechanisms is up to you.<br>Whether you're pursuing the strongest hands, crafting beautiful hands with dedication, or relentlessly collecting Dora, in <strong>Sky's The Limit MAH-JONG</strong>, you can immerse yourself in your own Mahjong game without any interference.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tile Trading</h2>Collect your preferred tiles at the trading shop, build your deck, and devise strategies to counteract luck.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/ab907fa099de667765251e435c001699.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/ab907fa099de667765251e435c001699.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/ab907fa099de667765251e435c001699.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Tiles</h2>Make effective use of special Dora and bonus tiles to gain an advantage in your games.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/c1f444f1d133976d6154ad3ae3eae299.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/c1f444f1d133976d6154ad3ae3eae299.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/c1f444f1d133976d6154ad3ae3eae299.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Possibilities with Deck Building</h2><strong>\"There is no need for only four of the same tile in the deck.\" </strong>Your choices can create hands that are impossible in reality!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/eb8a9b1d1415e4b72b95cfd1179810c7.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/eb8a9b1d1415e4b72b95cfd1179810c7.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/eb8a9b1d1415e4b72b95cfd1179810c7.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boost Status</h2>Manipulate the number of draws and discards, and even control the Dora to create the best environment to strengthen your hands.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/1ed23e16b0f4b2a47ad1c65ea59a93e1.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=500 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/1ed23e16b0f4b2a47ad1c65ea59a93e1.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/1ed23e16b0f4b2a47ad1c65ea59a93e1.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No-Ceiling Scoring System (Ao-Tenjo)</h2>Score calculation is based on the Ao-Tenjo rule, meaning points are not capped, and all the Fu and Han are reflected in the score. Ao-Tenjo means there is no upper limit to the points you can earn. It's your challenge to discover the \"highest score\" in this game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/0deee4421f854adfc65a6e3aa573faf2.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/0deee4421f854adfc65a6e3aa573faf2.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/0deee4421f854adfc65a6e3aa573faf2.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Round Selection</h2>Risk vs. Reward? Choose the rounds to challenge according to your strategy and earn the rewards you need.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/4709b3c05fdd2bc17a755c972d524d60.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=200 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/4709b3c05fdd2bc17a755c972d524d60.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/4709b3c05fdd2bc17a755c972d524d60.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless Mode</h2>As long as you continue to surpass the target score and want to keep winning, the challenges are limitless.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/876937cd2a78fb6a6122177a6ca603ab.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/876937cd2a78fb6a6122177a6ca603ab.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/876937cd2a78fb6a6122177a6ca603ab.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
