s you can earn. It's your challenge to discover the \"highest score\" in this game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/0deee4421f854adfc65a6e3aa573faf2.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/0deee4421f854adfc65a6e3aa573faf2.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/0deee4421f854adfc65a6e3aa573faf2.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Round Selection</h2>Risk vs. Reward? Choose the rounds to challenge according to your strategy and earn the rewards you need.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/4709b3c05fdd2bc17a755c972d524d60.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=200 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/4709b3c05fdd2bc17a755c972d524d60.webm?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/4709b3c05fdd2bc17a755c972d524d60.mp4?t=1731113891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless Mode</h2>As long as you continue to surpass the target score and want to keep winning, the challenges are limitless.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/876937cd2a78fb6a6122177a6ca603ab.poster.avif?t=1731113891\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085620/extras/876937cd2a78fb6a612217